    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm hearing a lot of talk about how these rules are basically just \"green\" idealism that doesn't account for real-world math. do you think there's any actual evidence that these regs provide a net economic benefit to the manufacturing sector, or are the costs pretty much just a one-way street for small shops?",
